<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Collingwood </h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Most of the Collingwood real estate units typically offer stunning mountain views and are located within close proximity of one of the several local parks in the neighborhood.</p>
            <p class="par-xl">One of the most popular and desired neighbourhoods for contemporary home buyers in the whole of NW Calgary.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">From massive local parks, biking trails, cross-country skiing to majestic fountains, tennis courts and even a golf course, Collingwood features an eclectic mix of recreational activities for its residents of varying tastes.</p>
        </div>
